we don't care that he's sexting.

15:57.206 --> 15:59.875
- We care how he votes.
- And they'll understand, give us the debate,

15:59.959 --> 16:03.253
let us use the format we want,
and we'll all go out for chocolate milkshakes.

16:03.379 --> 16:06.798
