but since there's sex involved,

16:14.390 --> 16:17.351
we can't deny its national importance.

16:17.435 --> 16:20.729
Especially since we don't know all
or even any of the facts.

16:23.232 --> 16:26.401
Three minutes.
I assume you want the pictures.

16:27.695 --> 16:29.821
Good meeting.

