17:17.870 --> 17:19.746
All she has to do is buy my contract,

17:19.831 --> 17:21.748
which she can do with the money
under her sofa cushions.

17:21.833 --> 17:23.625
But then she'd have to explain
why she was firing

17:23.710 --> 17:25.877
the second most watched anchor on cable

17:25.962 --> 17:27.796
and she can't do that.

17:28.089 --> 17:30.590
Is it a coincidence that
the tabloid stories about you

17:30.675 --> 17:31.967
started right after the election?

17:32.760 --> 17:34.136
