his audience isn't unreasonable,

17:51.738 --> 17:53.071
if that's what you're asking.

17:53.156 --> 17:55.157
It wasn't and you know it.

17:57.744 --> 18:00.620
You're trying to get me to write
this story without your fingerprints on it.

18:00.705 --> 18:04.541
AWM has to do business with Congress
and you're making it much harder.

18:04.625 --> 18:07.502
Leona wants you fired,
but can't do it unless she can explain it.

18:07.587 --> 18:09.880
She's hoping the tabloid stories
build to a critical mass

18:09.964 --> 18:12.632
or that your ratings tank.

18:12.967 --> 18:15.177
Say something if I'm wrong,
say nothing if I'm right.

18:19.515 --> 18:21.349
For what it's worth, I'd cave, too.

18:22.810 --> 18:26.855
