18:42.789 --> 18:45.290
The newsletters would get
a standing ovation at a Klan rally,

18:45.374 --> 18:47.042
but you should stop asking me
questions about them.

18:47.126 --> 18:49.211
- You need a better answer.
- He needs a better answer.

18:49.921 --> 18:52.047
Tell you what question I'd start off with.

18:52.173 --> 18:53.840
- Congresswoman Bachmann.
- Yes?

18:53.925 --> 18:57.052
You've said that you were told
