19:17.406 --> 19:19.908
What does his voice sound like?

19:20.159 --> 19:22.994
What did he say exactly, word for word?

19:23.079 --> 19:26.581
Did he speak in Hebrew?
Acadian? Kiswahili-Bantu?

19:26.707 --> 19:30.043
