19:30.336 --> 19:32.712
She's claiming to be a prophet.

19:32.797 --> 19:34.714
The whole world is sitting
on the edge of their seat.

19:34.799 --> 19:36.842
How is this not the first question Will asks?

19:36.926 --> 19:40.262
First of all, can you stop pointing at me
and saying she and her?

19:40.346 --> 19:41.930
You're the one who wanted to play a woman.

19:42.056 --> 19:43.306
But tell me why that question is out of line.

19:43.432 --> 19:46.226
Because it's not the best way
to demonstrate seriousness of intent

19:46.310 --> 19:48.353
and it's not the best way to not insult people.

19:48.479 --> 19:51.106
- Which people?
- Christians. 83% of the country.

19:51.357 --> 19:53.275
I'm one of them. And she's insulting me.

19:53.401 --> 19:55.527
Please, stop pointing at me when you are...

19:55.611 --> 19:58.446
Relax, J. Edgar. She's insulting me,

19:58.614 --> 20:01.283
she's insulting my family,
she's insulting my congregation,

20:01.409 --> 20:02.951
and she's insulting my faith.

20:03.286 --> 20:05.120
She's implying that Christians are imbeciles

20:05.204 --> 20:07.497
who will believe anything while reducing God

20:07.623 --> 20:10.208
to a party hack who endorses
political candidates.

20:10.376 --> 20:13.670
Now, maybe I'm wrong.
Maybe this is the first time since Moses

20:13.754 --> 20:16.882
that God has given direct
instructions to someone other than his son.

20:16.966 --> 20:18.884
But if so, I think it deserves a follow-up.

20:18.968 --> 20:21.595
We're not going to get the debate
if we're mocking their candidates.

20:21.679 --> 20:25.682
The whole point of the new debate format
is to compel the candidates to tell the truth

20:25.808 --> 20:27.559
and make them responsible
for their own rhetoric

20:27.643 --> 20:30.395
by asking tougher questions
than a Match.com profile.

20:30.605 --> 20:34.190
If she knows what God wants,
then I'm voting for her.

20:34.275 --> 20:35.942
If she doesn't, she should stop saying so.

20:36.027 --> 20:38.403
I'm not attacking Christians.
I'm defending them.

20:38.487 --> 20:40.363
- All right.
- Just a moment, please.

20:40.448 --> 20:41.448
What?

20:41.532 --> 20:43.158
I'm standing up for the
tens of millions of Christians

20:43.242 --> 20:46.578
who are tired of being represented
by having our identity...

20:46.662 --> 20:48.496
There's been an identity theft.

20:48.998 --> 20:50.999
That's it. That's the one I want.

20:52.501 --> 20:57.047
