20:57.298 --> 20:59.341
Does anyone have a problem with that?

20:59.550 --> 21:02.302
All right, well, we lost almost
half a million viewers

21:02.386 --> 21:03.970
to Nancy Grace last week.

21:04.347 --> 21:06.181
