to give a report card

21:41.384 --> 21:42.467
on Obama's union relationships.

21:42.551 --> 21:45.261
Will the AFL-CIO still
be sour on him tomorrow?

21:45.346 --> 21:47.472
- I don't know.
- Let's find out.

21:48.265 --> 21:51.559
All right, to give us
a crash course in how best

21:51.644 --> 21:53.812
to exploit this tragedy
and to erase all boundaries

21:53.896 --> 21:55.772
of what should be used as entertainment,

21:56.399 --> 21:59.359
I've enlisted the help
of a master of the dark arts.

21:59.443 --> 22:00.902
I understand I'm needed.

22:02.154 --> 22:05.115
- Thank you.
- Forget everything you know about the news.

22:05.199 --> 22:07.075
