23:03.966 --> 23:05.633
Charlie.

23:09.263 --> 23:10.972
That has to have been strange for you.

23:11.098 --> 23:13.892
That's going to be a story you'll tell later.

23:16.896 --> 23:18.146
Late for Dinner?

23:18.230 --> 23:21.149
