23:25.571 --> 23:29.824
No, but it's usually the international sign for...

23:29.992 --> 23:31.242
Doesn't matter.

23:31.368 --> 23:33.453
I'm a busy guy
and if you're faffin' me around...

23:33.579 --> 23:35.455
Would you mind taking the battery
out of your cell phone?

23:35.539 --> 23:38.083
The walls in the New York Public Library
are three feet thick.

23:38.167 --> 23:39.334
That's why we're meeting here,

23:39.418 --> 23:41.419
but I'd like you to take the battery
out of your cell phone.

23:41.504 --> 23:43.630
You have reason to believe
you're under surveillance?

23:43.714 --> 23:46.007
Everyone's under surveillance.
If you've got a cell phone...

23:46.092 --> 23:47.759
