23:47.843 --> 23:50.595
Did I or did I not establish
credibility on May 1 st?

23:50.888 --> 23:54.641
You correctly predicted that
we'd all be called to work, yes.

23:54.892 --> 23:57.435
Sometimes at the NSA,
we download a rolling bug

23:57.520 --> 24:00.814
onto smartphones to slave the microphone.

24:01.899 --> 24:04.275
You ever get an unwanted text message?

24:04.360 --> 24:06.194
All the time, but they're from my boss.

24:07.154 --> 24:09.656
Here.

24:10.199 --> 24:12.242
I'll never be able to put that back together.

24:12.368 --> 24:14.452
They're coming out with
a better model in six months.

24:14.745 --> 24:17.372
That's unusual for the tech industry.

24:18.332 --> 24:19.791
Can you tell me a little about yourself?

24:20.751 --> 24:23.419
I started out chasing around
a Soviet Pacific Fleet

24:23.546 --> 24:26.214
doing signal intelligence
cryptology for the Navy.

24:27.049 --> 24:30.927
But when the Berlin Wall
came down, my war was over.

24:31.053 --> 24:33.972
So I went into the private sector
like everybody else in the '90s,

24:34.056 --> 24:35.223
only not for a dot-com,

24:35.891 --> 24:38.893
doing data compression for fiber optics.

24:38.978 --> 24:41.396
Then 9/11 happened and I decided

24:41.564 --> 24:44.315
it was a good time to get back into
public service hunting bad guys.

24:44.400 --> 24:45.483
You're an IT guy.

24:45.568 --> 24:48.153
My title is Assistant Deputy Director

24:48.237 --> 24:51.781
of Technology and Systems Cryptology
and Mathematics at NSA.

24:56.537 --> 24:57.996
I'm gonna have to...

25:01.041 --> 25:02.625
I product-test software.

25:03.419 --> 25:05.879
- NSA software?
- Yes, sir.

25:05.963 --> 25:07.255
Can you tell me about the software?

25:08.966 --> 25:10.425
It's data mining.

25:10.509 --> 25:13.178
One of the ways the NSA
was tracking bin Laden,

25:13.262 --> 25:15.054
or any terrorist for that matter,

25:15.139 --> 25:19.934
was to write code that would sift through
millions of electronic communications

25:20.060 --> 25:22.312
looking for a needle in a giant haystack.

25:23.189 --> 25:25.523
You know the machine that Batman
uses in The Dark Knight

25:25.608 --> 25:27.942
to find the Joker, but when Morgan Freeman
finds out about it,

25:28.027 --> 25:30.987
he says, "I'm quitting because no man
should have this much power"?

25:31.947 --> 25:33.698
- No.
- "No" what?

25:33.782 --> 25:35.658
I do not know that machine.

25:35.743 --> 25:37.952
Well, it exists.

25:38.245 --> 25:40.997
We gave the contract to
two defense contracting big boys

25:41.123 --> 25:43.625
and it was my job mostly
to make sure that they delivered

25:43.792 --> 25:45.001
and that it worked.

25:45.127 --> 25:48.004
The project title is GLOBALCLARITY

25:48.339 --> 25:54.010
and it intercepts 1.7 billion phone calls,
emails, and texts every day.

25:54.386 --> 25:55.929
- Legally?
- By what standard?

25:56.138 --> 25:57.805
- The law.
- No.

25:57.973 --> 26:02.560
It involves a significant amount of illegal,
warrantless wiretapping of American citizens.

26:02.645 --> 26:08.233
Just to be... When you say "warrantless,"
are you saying "unnecessary"?

26:08.317 --> 26:10.526
"Without a warrant." Warrantless.

26:10.819 --> 26:13.154
We could hunt for terrorists legally,

26:13.239 --> 26:15.907
but due to our bosses'
devotion to GLOBALCLARITY,

26:15.991 --> 26:19.285
the NSA has been happily
violating the Fourth Amendment,

26:19.453 --> 26:21.496
USSID 18,

26:21.580 --> 26:26.000
and about a dozen of the NSA's
own regulations about spying on Americans.

26:26.085 --> 26:31.839
You've got guys listening in on ex-wives,
dropping in on calls from soldiers overseas,

26:32.091 --> 26:34.259
checking out what movie stars are up to.

26:34.343 --> 26:36.427
Am I the first person
you've talked to about this?

26:36.512 --> 26:39.847
No, stop confusing me with
Donald Sutherland in JFK.

26:39.932 --> 26:41.724
Well, a second ago,
you were Morgan Freeman.

26:41.809 --> 26:43.268
I have testified in front of Congress

26:43.352 --> 26:46.187
and to the Pentagon Inspector General.
I got nowhere.

26:46.272 --> 26:48.731
Nobody on the Hill wants
to admit it's fucked up

26:48.857 --> 26:52.568
because nobody wants to
be seen as post-9/11 soft.

26:53.779 --> 26:55.321
Where does AWM come in?

26:55.447 --> 26:57.907
Atlantis World Media
owns Atlantis Cable News.

26:58.325 --> 27:01.202
- Yeah.
