27:32.026 --> 27:37.613
Reese Lansing is James Murdoch,
but Lansing's been ordering it.

27:38.741 --> 27:40.158
Digested yet?

27:45.205 --> 27:46.372
These classified?

27:46.457 --> 27:48.833
