to violate the Espionage Act.

27:49.293 --> 27:51.419
These are just transcripts of my testimony

27:51.545 --> 27:54.088
before the House subcommittee
and the Pentagon.

27:54.423 --> 27:57.884
Vet me, vet the material.
Take all the time you need.

27:58.302 --> 27:59.844
Why are you whistle-blowing?

28:01.638 --> 28:03.931
I fought the Soviets.

28:04.016 --> 28:06.309
The way that government made
their people live their lives

28:06.393 --> 28:09.187
was a very good reason to fight them.

28:09.355 --> 28:13.733
After 9/11,
we started doing the exact same thing.

28:14.276 --> 28:18.029
I didn't spend my life fighting Communists
to have it come to this.

28:19.490 --> 28:21.449
Report on GLOBALCLARITY.

28:21.533 --> 28:23.701
And once I see that report,
I'll give you what you need

28:23.786 --> 28:25.620
to protect yourself from Leona Lansing.

28:25.996 --> 28:28.581
How do you know we need
protecting from Leona Lansing?

28:28.707 --> 28:31.334
Have you been listening? 'Cause we have.

28:51.688 --> 28:53.981
This woman is the best I've ever seen.

28:54.108 --> 28:55.566
Center screen is Nancy.

28:55.692 --> 28:57.777
These three corners are live feeds of
the guest experts.

28:57.861 --> 29:00.405
- What are they experts in?
- Agreeing with everything Nancy says.

29:00.489 --> 29:02.031
- But what keeps your attention...
- Excuse me.

29:04.201 --> 29:06.285
This is Brian Brenner, everyone.

29:06.370 --> 29:08.663
It's possible he's going to
be writing a feature on 2.0.

29:08.747 --> 29:11.124
